Ex parte: In the Matter of Banco Territorial y Agricola de Puerta Rico and *741the Banco Commercial de Puerto Rico, Trustees, Petitioners. Submitted November 17, 1913. Decided December 1, 1913. Mr. Frederic D. McKenney and Mr. Francis H. Dexter for the petitioners.
